Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:08.45,Chn,,0,0,0,,没关系 没关系 这不是真的\N{\rEng}It's okay. It's okay. It's not real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:10.12,Chn,,0,0,0,,没 没 没有任何事是真的\N{\rEng}N-n-n-n-nothing's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.06,Chn,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 孩子\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:13.19,Chn,,0,0,0,,没 没 没关系 你不是真的\N{\rEng}I-I-it's okay. You aren't real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:17.73,Chn,,0,0,0,,天 你是对的 我应该多多自由发挥的\N{\rEng}God, you're right. I should do more freeform stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:19.73,Chn,,0,0,0,,- 走你 - 发生了什么\N{\rEng}In you go. What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:23.40,Chn,,0,0,0,,我把你带到这的理由 是要用你无限的潜能\N{\rEng}The reason I brought you here. I'll now fuel my anthology with your
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:28.57,Chn,,0,0,0,,充满我的选集 把它推向最后一站 冲破第五面墙\N{\rEng}limitless potential, propelling it to its final stop -- beyond the fifth wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:32.95,Chn,,0,0,0,,你个蠢货 我们的潜能不是无限的\N{\rEng}You idiot. Our potential isn't limitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:34.28,Chn,,0,0,0,,你就算把我们耗尽\N{\rEng}You'll never break the fifth wall
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.28,0:14:35.41,Chn,,0,0,0,,也永远无法打破第五面墙\N{\rEng}before you've burnt us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:38.22,Chn,,0,0,0,,是这样吗 行吧 双赢\N{\rEng}Is that so? Oh, well. Win-win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:39.49,Chn,,0,0,0,,Rick 他要做什么\N{\rEng}Rick, w-what's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:41.15,Chn,,0,0,0,,他想接入我们的思维 Morty\N{\rEng}He's trying to tap into us, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:42.89,Chn,,0,0,0,,扛住\N{\rEng}Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:45.02,Chn,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信你终于要去上大学了\N{\rEng}I can't believe you're finally headed off to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:48.09,Chn,,0,0,0,,是啊 你也知道 确实有种 你永远停留在17岁的错觉\N{\rEng}Yeah, you know, it really felt like you were gonna be 17 forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:50.16,Chn,,0,0,0,,停了 差不多 至少16年\N{\rEng}For, like, 16 years, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:52.10,Chn,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信我会为这件事流泪\N{\rEng}I can't believe I'm tearing up over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:54.63,Chn,,0,0,0,,老天 Rick 你知道吗 你真的柔和了很多\N{\rEng}Jesus, Rick, you know, you've really softened up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.37,Chn,,0,0,0,,这是人之常情 Morty\N{\rEng}It's a human moment, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.90,Chn,,0,0,0,,人之常情\N{\rEng}It's a human moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:59.94,Chn,,0,0,0,,啊 疼\N{\rEng}Aaah! Aaah! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.85,0:15:07.85,Chn,,0,0,0,,阿道夫·林肯勒 我以为你死了\N{\rEng}Abradolph lincoler? I thought you were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:11.12,Chn,,0,0,0,,我活着 并且我需要你的帮忙\N{\rEng}I'm very much alive, and I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:12.25,Chn,,0,0,0,,耶\N{\rEng}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:13.92,Chn,,0,0,0,,草 他拿走了好东西 Morty\N{\rEng}Shit he's taking the good stuff, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:15.66,Chn,,0,0,0,,等等 这些是有官方盖章的吗\N{\rEng}Wait, is -- is any of this canon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:16.79,Chn,,0,0,0,,本来能有的\N{\rEng}It could have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:18.32,Chn,,0,0,0,,哦 天\N{\rEng}oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:21.53,Chn,,0,0,0,,竟然还有Rick Sanchez珍视的东西吗\N{\rEng}Are there things Rick Sanchez holds sacred after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:29.54,Chn,,0,0,0,,你是怎么找到我们的\N{\rEng}How did you find us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:32.20,Chn,,0,0,0,,我曾信任你\N{\rEng}I trusted you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:34.61,Chn,,0,0,0,,别因为你自己的错误决定怪罪别人\N{\rEng}Don't blame others for your bad decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:38.74,Chn,,0,0,0,,扛住 Morty 在他耗尽我们之前扛住\N{\rEng}Resist, Morty! Resist before he burns us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:40.48,Chn,,0,0,0,,哦 太迟了\N{\rEng}Oh, too late now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.81,Chn,,0,0,0,,怎么了 Rick\N{\rEng}What's wrong, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:44.08,Chn,,0,0,0,,你不想看看你的故事是什么结局吗\N{\rEng}Don't you want to see how your story ends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:15:59.57,Chn,,0,0,0,,我操 Rick 我们怎么\N{\rEng}Holy shit, Rick. What do we --
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:00.77,Chn,,0,0,0,,没没 没路可逃了\N{\rEng}There -- there -- there's now way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:01.97,Chn,,0,0,0,,你说对了 Morty\N{\rEng}You're right, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:03.70,Chn,,0,0,0,,有时候真的是无路可走\N{\rEng}Sometimes it does seem like there's no way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:05.24,Chn,,0,0,0,,毫无希望的样子\N{\rEng}Like it's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:07.51,Chn,,0,0,0,,但是记住 总有人为我们守候\N{\rEng}But remember, there's always someone there for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:08.84,Chn,,0,0,0,,谁\N{\rEng}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:10.11,Chn,,0,0,0,,我最好的朋友以及私人救星\N{\rEng}My best friend and personal savior,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:11.18,Chn,,0,0,0,,耶稣\N{\rEng}Jesus christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:12.78,Chn,,0,0,0,,什么鬼 你都不信上帝的\N{\rEng}What?! You -- you don't believe in god.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:14.18,Chn,,0,0,0,,但他相信我们\N{\rEng}But he believes in us, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:15.92,Chn,,0,0,0,,你懂吗 我以为我是造物主\N{\rEng}You know, I thought I was the inventor,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:18.85,Chn,,0,0,0,,但是最伟大的创造 是永恒生命的馈赠\N{\rEng}but the greatest invention of all is the free gift of eternal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.85,Chn,,0,0,0,,什么 你在他妈搞我吧\N{\rEng}Is this -- are you fucking with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:22.39,Chn,,0,0,0,,噢 相信我 Morty\N{\rEng}oh, trust me, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:24.26,Chn,,0,0,0,,我这一生搞砸了很多事情\N{\rEng}I've done plenty of effed up stuff in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:26.66,Chn,,0,0,0,,但接纳耶稣从来不会晚\N{\rEng}But it's never too late to accept Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:28.19,Chn,,0,0,0,,耶稣永远在敲门\N{\rEng}Jesus is always knocking at the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.80,Chn,,0,0,0,,我们只需要敞开那扇门\N{\rEng}All we have to do is open it and let him
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.00,Chn,,0,0,0,,- 将他迎接到我们心里 - 怎么做呢\N{\rEng}into our hearts. How?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:32.66,Chn,,0,0,0,,你问得真好 Morty\N{\rEng}I'm so glad you asked, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:34.67,Chn,,0,0,0,,就闭上眼睛 向他祈祷\N{\rEng}Just close your eyes and go to him in prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:36.07,Chn,,0,0,0,,像这样\N{\rEng}Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:37.67,Chn,,0,0,0,,- 天父 - 天父\N{\rEng}Heavenly father. Heavenly father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:39.54,Chn,,0,0,0,,感谢赐予我们你的独生子\N{\rEng}Thank you for sending your only begotten son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:41.54,Chn,,0,0,0,,等一下 你们这是在干什么\N{\rEng}What a second, no! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:43.68,Chn,,0,0,0,,耶稣 我向你敞开心扉\N{\rEng}Jesus, I accept you into my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:45.08,Chn,,0,0,0,,不 这太差劲了\N{\rEng}No! This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:46.88,Chn,,0,0,0,,停下来啊 你们绝对不会这么干的\N{\rEng}Stop! You guys would never do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.15,Chn,,0,0,0,,用你的精神把我填满\N{\rEng}Fill me with your spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.95,Chn,,0,0,0,,让我成为你闪光的山上的城\N{\rEng}Make me a shining city on a hill for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:51.82,Chn,,0,0,0,,- 别 别 - 让我重生\N{\rEng}-No! No! -Make me born again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:53.69,Chn,,0,0,0,,- 别 - 以耶稣之名 我们祈祷\N{\rEng}-No! -In jesus' name, we pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:54.95,Chn,,0,0,0,,- 阿门 - 阿们\N{\rEng}-Amen. -Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:56.69,Chn,,0,0,0,,- 阿门 - 你做到了\N{\rEng}-Amen! -You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:16:58.02,Chn,,0,0,0,,- 真棒 Morty - 架架\N{\rEng}Way to go, Morty! Crossy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:16:59.22,Chn,,0,0,0,,圣经蜥蜴 你们来啦\N{\rEng}Bible-saurus. You made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:01.36,Chn,,0,0,0,,我们可绝对不能错过这个呀\N{\rEng}We wouldn't miss this for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:02.63,Chn,,0,0,0,,说得没错 芹菜先生\N{\rEng}You said it, mr. Celery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:04.56,Chn,,0,0,0,,这他妈都是什么鬼\N{\rEng}What the fuck is all of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:06.50,Chn,,0,0,0,,这是最伟大的故事 故事之主\N{\rEng}Greatest story ever told, story lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.50,Chn,,0,0,0,,不 不是的 这太垃圾了\N{\rEng}No, it's not. It's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.57,Chn,,0,0,0,,请你再说一遍\N{\rEng}I beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:15.04,Chn,,0,0,0,,我靠\N{\rEng}Goddamn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:16.91,Chn,,0,0,0,,我的天 我的神\N{\rEng}my lord and my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:20.51,Chn,,0,0,0,,-不 不 这里太烂了 - 我们赶快他妈离开这里 走 快\N{\rEng}-No! No! It sucks in here. -Let's get the fuck outta here. Go, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.91,Chn,,0,0,0,,啊 我们安全了 Morty\N{\rEng}Ugh. We're safe, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:23.58,Chn,,0,0,0,,没人想看那种鬼东西\N{\rEng}Nobody ever wanted to see that shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:25.25,Chn,,0,0,0,,故 故事之主会怎么样?\N{\rEng}Wh-what's gonna happen to story lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:27.79,Chn,,0,0,0,,他搞不好要在所有作家的地狱里熬到永恒\N{\rEng}He gets to spend eternity in every writer's hell --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:30.92,Chn,,0,0,0,,- 也就是圣经里 - 不好说诶 有些人还真喜欢这种东西\N{\rEng}The bible. I don't know. Some people actually like that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:32.39,Chn,,0,0,0,,看起来有点愤世嫉俗\N{\rEng}Seems kind of cynical.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:33.99,Chn,,0,0,0,,我只是不喜欢烂招 你懂吗\N{\rEng}I just don't like taking cheap shots, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:37.33,Chn,,0,0,0,,烂招 Morty 我们完完全全是被耶稣救了\N{\rEng}Cheap shots? Morty, we were literally saved by jesus christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:39.13,Chn,,0,0,0,,你说说 这哪里冒犯了\N{\rEng}Tell me in any way how that's offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:40.60,Chn,,0,0,0,,这虽然有点迷惑\N{\rEng}This was a little confusing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.80,Chn,,0,0,0,,但可能这个拉近了我们的关系 不是吗\N{\rEng}but I guess it brought us closer together, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.20,Chn,,0,0,0,,考验了我们的心魔\N{\rEng}Tested our demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.94,Chn,,0,0,0,,让我们更加相信自己\N{\rEng}Made us believe in ourselves more than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:47.21,Chn,,0,0,0,,对咯 你说的对 Morty\N{\rEng}Yeah. You're right, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:50.81,Chn,,0,0,0,,我们总算用meta的套路把那些官方盖章的同人烂事给演完了 现在可以做自己了\N{\rEng}We got all that meta-canon shit outta the way and now we can just be ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:52.74,Chn,,0,0,0,,现在我们来把这辆火车\N{\rEng}Now what do you say we bring this train
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:54.41,Chn,,0,0,0,,开进车站吧\N{\rEng}into the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:06.16,Chn,,0,0,0,,我操\N{\rEng}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:07.89,Chn,,0,0,0,,你觉得咋样\N{\rEng}So what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:09.16,Chn,,0,0,0,,哇 你从哪里弄来这个东西的\N{\rEng}Wow. Where did you get this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:10.96,Chn,,0,0,0,,瑞城的礼品店\N{\rEng}The citadel of Ricks gift shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:13.70,Chn,,0,0,0,,你真的喜欢这个吗 我觉得你根本都不在意\N{\rEng}Do you really like it? I didn't think you'd even care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.84,Chn,,0,0,0,,什么 Morty 不 我爱死了\N{\rEng}What? Morty. No. I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.57,Chn,,0,0,0,,你做了最重要的事情\N{\rEng}You did the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:18.97,Chn,,0,0,0,,你 你买了些东西\N{\rEng}You -- you bought something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.31,Chn,,0,0,0,,- 什么 - 你买了些东西\N{\rEng}What? You bought something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:23.04,Chn,,0,0,0,,用钱 天呐 我太爱钱了 Morty\N{\rEng}With money. God. I love money so much, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:25.04,Chn,,0,0,0,,- 你在讽刺我吗 - 购物 Morty\N{\rEng}Are you being sarcastic? Merchandise, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:27.91,Chn,,0,0,0,,你人生的唯一目标就是买买买和消耗商品\N{\rEng}Your only purpose in life is to buy and consume merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.32,Chn,,0,0,0,,你做到了 你去了个商店\N{\rEng}And you did it. You went into a store --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:32.18,Chn,,0,0,0,,一个真真正正的商店 然后你买了些东西\N{\rEng}An actual honest to god store -- and you bought something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:34.19,Chn,,0,0,0,,你没有问问题 或者提出道德上的抱怨\N{\rEng}You didn't ask questions or raise ethical complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.19,0:18:36.12,Chn,,0,0,0,,你 你就直视着资本主义的獠牙\N{\rEng}You -- you just looked straight into the bleeding jaws
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:38.66,Chn,,0,0,0,,然后说 “是的 爸爸 来吧”\N{\rEng}of capitalism and said "yes, daddy, please."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.93,Chn,,0,0,0,,所以我 我为你感到骄傲\N{\rEng}And I'm... I'm so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:42.33,Chn,,0,0,0,,我只希望你能买多一点\N{\rEng}I only wish you could've bought more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:44.93,Chn,,0,0,0,,我 我太爱买东西了 Morty\N{\rEng}I -- I love buying things so much, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:46.20,Chn,,0,0,0,,Rick 你 你是不是\N{\rEng}Rick, are -- are you --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:47.40,Chn,,0,0,0,,你要不要去趟医院\N{\rEng}Do you need to go to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:49.94,Chn,,0,0,0,,我爱你 Morty 来给姥爷一个吻\N{\rEng}I love you, Morty. Give grandpa a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:51.67,Chn,,0,0,0,,来 来 来给 给姥爷一个吻\N{\rEng}Give -- give -- gimme -- give grandpa a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:53.01,Chn,,0,0,0,,你可以亲嘴巴\N{\rEng}Lips if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:54.54,Chn,,0,0,0,,亲哪都行 看你怎么舒服\N{\rEng}What-- whatever you're comfortable with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:55.81,Chn,,0,0,0,,有些文化里就这么做\N{\rEng}Some cultures do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:18:57.41,Chn,,0,0,0,,你真好 谢谢你\N{\rEng}That was sweet. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:19:00.15,Chn,,0,0,0,,我 我爱你 你是我的小伙伴\N{\rEng}I -- I love you. You're my little buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:01.81,Chn,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:03.08,Chn,,0,0,0,,我们看看跨维度有线电视吧\N{\rEng}Let's watch some interdimensional cable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:10.36,Chn,,0,0,0,,你的意思是我的父\N{\rEng}So you're saying my father
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:11.76,Chn,,0,0,0,,和他的国\N{\rEng}and his kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:14.76,Chn,,0,0,0,,嗯 是的 都是基于\N{\rEng}Well, yes -- it's based on the fusion
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:16.23,Chn,,0,0,0,,一个叫做“野”的苏美尔神\N{\rEng}of a Sumerian god named "Ya"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:18.90,Chn,,0,0,0,,和叫做“火华”的美索不达米亚神的融合\N{\rEng}and a Mesopotamian god named "Way."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:21.63,Chn,,0,0,0,,所以我们现在在一个玩具火车里吗\N{\rEng}And we're in a toy train?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:22.97,Chn,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:26.11,Chn,,0,0,0,,真是让人怀疑万物的存在性了 对吧\N{\rEng}It's enough to really make you question all of existence, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:28.71,Chn,,0,0,0,,那你会怎么做呢\N{\rEng}So what do you think you're gonna do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:32.04,Chn,,0,0,0,,我会做我一直做的\N{\rEng}I'm gonna do what I've always done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:33.91,Chn,,0,0,0,,我会他妈的离开这里\N{\rEng}I'm gonna get the fuck outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:38.52,Chn,,0,0,0,,万千预兆之父啊 请赐我超越视界之血\N{\rEng}Father of omens! Give me blood beyond sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:42.45,Chn,,0,0,0,,喂 怎么回事 Morty\N{\rEng}Hey, what the fuck Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:44.19,Chn,,0,0,0,,你买的小火车刚自己脱了轨\N{\rEng}The train you got me just completely derailed itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:45.86,Chn,,0,0,0,,上面的窗户涂满了血\N{\rEng}There's blood all over the windows on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:47.93,Chn,,0,0,0,,噢 很抱歉 Rick 我拿去退了吧\N{\rEng}Oh, man, I'm sorry, Rick. I guess I'll return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:49.19,Chn,,0,0,0,,退了 你疯了吗\N{\rEng}Return -- are you insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:50.66,Chn,,0,0,0,,你没听到我刚说的吗\N{\rEng}Did you hear nothing I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:51.86,Chn,,0,0,0,,再买一个 Morty\N{\rEng}Buy another one, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.20,Chn,,0,0,0,,消费 Morty\N{\rEng}Consume, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:55.20,Chn,,0,0,0,,因为这傻逼病毒没人他妈的出门购物了\N{\rEng}Nobody's out there shopping with this fucking virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:57.27,Chn,,0,0,0,,你钱包他妈去哪了?\N{\rEng}Where's your fucking wallet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:29.10,Chn,,0,0,0,,对那单调的冒险\N{\rEng}Tired of the same boring adventures
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:30.17,Chn,,0,0,0,,和你狗屎般的Morty 感到无聊了吗\N{\rEng}with your dogshit Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:31.90,Chn,,0,0,0,,- 对啊 - 噢 天呐\N{\rEng}Yeah! Aw. Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:34.37,Chn,,0,0,0,,那么准备好体验瑞城的故事小火车吧\N{\rEng}Then get ready for the citadel of Rick's story train.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:36.11,Chn,,0,0,0,,故事小火车 故事小火车\N{\rEng}Story train. Story train.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:37.44,Chn,,0,0,0,,瑞城的故事小火车\N{\rEng}The citadel of Rick's story train
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:39.71,Chn,,0,0,0,,装满一车厢一车厢的敌人 爱人\N{\rEng}comes with car after car of enemies, lovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:41.11,Chn,,0,0,0,,还有Goomby 全部都和\N{\rEng}and Goomby, all grappling with
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:42.25,Chn,,0,0,0,,你的本质缠绕在一起\N{\rEng}the nature of who you truly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:43.85,Chn,,0,0,0,,Rick是神 请出示票据\N{\rEng}Rick is a god! Tickets please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:45.58,Chn,,0,0,0,,哇哦 小心 故事之主来了\N{\rEng}Whoa! Watch out! It's story lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:46.92,Chn,,0,0,0,,我去 他好壮\N{\rEng}Damn. He's jacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:48.32,Chn,,0,0,0,,醇正的精槽\N{\rEng}Pure cum gutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:49.99,Chn,,0,0,0,,当然了 没有《最伟大的故事》的总设计师\N{\rEng}And of course, what story would be complete
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.92,Chn,,0,0,0,,哪有故事算是完整的\N{\rEng}without the engineer of the greatest story ever told.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.13,Chn,,0,0,0,,哇 耶稣\N{\rEng}Oh, jesus christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:55.80,Chn,,0,0,0,,我不是来指摘这个世界的 我是来拯救它的\N{\rEng}I have come not to judge the world, but to save it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:57.60,Chn,,0,0,0,,最棒的是 乐趣永不停\N{\rEng}And the best part is, the fun never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.33,Chn,,0,0,0,,多亏了 Rick 独家选集生成器\N{\rEng}Thanks to the Rick-patented anthology generator,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:00.87,Chn,,0,0,0,,你永远不会没有新的故事\N{\rEng}you'll never run out of new stories
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:02.00,Chn,,0,0,0,,及听故事的人\N{\rEng}and people to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:03.27,Chn,,0,0,0,,他们是活的吗 当然是\N{\rEng}Are they alive? Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.27,0:21:04.67,Chn,,0,0,0,,不过他们活不活无关紧要的\N{\rEng}But not in any ways that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:06.27,Chn,,0,0,0,,他们 没有 灵魂\N{\rEng}They. Have. No. Souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:07.61,Chn,,0,0,0,,命运 的 木偶\N{\rEng}Puppets. Of. Fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:09.14,Chn,,0,0,0,,故事小火车\N{\rEng}The story train.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:10.74,Chn,,0,0,0,,现于瑞城有售\N{\rEng}Available now in the citadel of Ricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:12.34,Chn,,0,0,0,,嘲讽地买它 真挚地买它 买它就对了\N{\rEng}Buy it ironically. Buy it sincerely. Just buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:13.55,Chn,,0,0,0,,你不买它也要买它\N{\rEng}Not buying it is an act of buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:14.95,Chn,,0,0,0,,现在就买它 赶紧去查查 是真的\N{\rEng}Buy it now. Look it up. It's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:16.68,Chn,,0,0,0,,www.story-train.com\N{\rEng}www.story-train.Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:18.82,Chn,,0,0,0,,就在网上 就在那 买它 买下这个火车\N{\rEng}On the internet. It's there. Buy it. Buy the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:20.35,Chn,,0,0,0,,我们要你买这个火车\N{\rEng}We want you to buy the train.